</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">➤SCP-4464-&nbsp;Dogs&nbsp;Could&nbsp;Be&nbsp;Bigger&nbsp;(JamCon&nbsp;2019)</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▼SCP-4464-&nbsp;Dogs&nbsp;Could&nbsp;Be&nbsp;Bigger</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><a href="/scp-4464">SCP-4464- Dogs Could Be Bigger</a><br />
This one was written for the first entry in Jamcon 2019, &quot;Shaggy dog&quot;. I had never heard of a shaggy dog tale at that point, so literally all I had was &quot;dogs&quot;. The entire process of how the idea developed can be found in the following chat log:</p>
<p>&lt;Mortos&gt; idea: its like a huge dog<br />
