&lt;Mortos&gt; like 600m tall<br />
&lt;Mortos&gt; also it lives on the moon<br />
&lt;MaliceAF&gt; sounds pretty compelling ngl<br />
&lt;MaliceAF&gt; gotta love a tall doggo<br />
&lt;MaliceAF&gt; although<br />
&lt;MaliceAF&gt; .s very tall things<br />
&lt;Secretary_Helen&gt; MaliceAF: SCP-2256: Very Tall Things (Rating: +411. Written 3 years ago By: qntm) - <a href="http://scp-wiki.net/scp-2256">http://scp-wiki.net/scp-2256</a><br />
&lt;Mortos&gt; those things are way taller than 600m<br />
